room_title: Escape room "Insane Asylum II" by PanIQ Room in Washington, D.C.
room_description: The year is 1956. You have been kidnapped by the CIA and being used as a guinea-pig for their mind control program known as MK-ULTRA. Doctors have held you inside a padded room for weeks now. There was an emergency at the other side of the institution, so the staff is gone for a while. Probably this is your last chance to escape before they completely brainwash you.
